abstract: A March 9 trial date has been set for an Arizona man accused of making a threatening phone call to California U.S. Rep. Adam Schiff last year.
snippet: A March 9 trial date has been set for an Arizona man accused of making a threatening phone call to California U.S. Rep. Adam Schiff last year.
lead_paragraph: TUCSON, Ariz. — A March 9 trial date has been set for an Arizona man accused of making a threatening phone call to California U.S. Rep. Adam Schiff last year.
headline_main: Arizona Man Accused of Threatening Congressman Adam Schiff
headline_print_headline: Arizona Man Accused of Threatening Congressman Adam Schiff

abstract: The "great American comeback” President Donald Trump claimed in his State of the Union speech drew on falsehoods about U.S. energy supremacy, health care and the economy as well as distortions about his predecessor's record.
snippet: The "great American comeback” President Donald Trump claimed in his State of the Union speech drew on falsehoods about U.S. energy supremacy, health care and the economy as well as distortions about his predecessor's record.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The "great American comeback” President Donald Trump claimed in his State of the Union speech drew on falsehoods about U.S. energy supremacy, health care and the economy as well as distortions about his predecessor's record.
headline_main: AP FACT CHECK: Trump's Exaggerated 'Great American Comeback'
headline_print_headline: AP FACT CHECK: Trump's Exaggerated 'Great American Comeback'

abstract: Buttigieg and Sanders were triumphant. But Trump had a few things he wanted to say for himself.
snippet: Buttigieg and Sanders were triumphant. But Trump had a few things he wanted to say for himself.
lead_paragraph: Bret Stephens: Just when I thought the Iowa caucus, and maybe the Democratic nomination, was in the bag for Bernie Sanders, Pete Buttigieg pulled out what looks to be either a largely unpredicted first-place finish in the Hawkeye State or at least a close second-place.

abstract: Venezuelan opposition leader Juan Guaidó drew a standing ovation from Republicans and Democrats in a rare moment of political unity as President Donald Trump delivered his State of the Union speech Tuesday.
snippet: Venezuelan opposition leader Juan Guaidó drew a standing ovation from Republicans and Democrats in a rare moment of political unity as President Donald Trump delivered his State of the Union speech Tuesday.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — Venezuelan opposition leader Juan Guaidó drew a standing ovation from Republicans and Democrats in a rare moment of political unity as President Donald Trump delivered his State of the Union speech Tuesday.

abstract: As he ramps up his re-election effort, the president has exaggerated or been inaccurate in discussing the economy, trade, Iran and his pressure campaign against Ukraine.
snippet: As he ramps up his re-election effort, the president has exaggerated or been inaccurate in discussing the economy, trade, Iran and his pressure campaign against Ukraine.
lead_paragraph: President Trump will deliver his third State of the Union address on Tuesday night, a day before the Senate is expected to acquit him in the impeachment trial.
headline_main: Trump brings a record of erroneous statements into his address.
